# Technology Adoption Trends

**Emerging technologies reshaping the market**

::: info
**Technology Adoption by Priority:**
- **Artificial Intelligence** - 78% planning implementation (2025)
- **API-First Architecture** - 71% prioritizing integration flexibility
- **Zero-Trust Security** - 69% upgrading security frameworks
- **Edge Computing** - 52% exploring distributed processing
- **Blockchain Integration** - 34% investigating use cases
- **Augmented Reality** - 18% considering collaboration features
:::

**AI adoption timeline accelerating due to competitive pressure**

@notes:
- AI becoming table stakes for competitive positioning
- API-first reflects integration-focused buying criteria
- Security upgrades driven by compliance requirements
- Edge computing addresses performance needs
- Blockchain still experimental for most organizations

