# Digital Transformation Impact

**How transformation initiatives affect software needs**

::: info
**Digital Transformation Status:**
- **Advanced Stage** - 23% of organizations
- **Active Implementation** - 45% of organizations  
- **Planning Phase** - 28% of organizations
- **Not Started** - 4% of organizations
:::

| Transformation Stage | Budget Allocation | Timeline | Technology Focus |
|---------------------|-------------------|----------|------------------|
| **Advanced** | 35% of IT budget | Continuous | Innovation & optimization |
| **Implementation** | 28% of IT budget | 18-24 months | Core system modernization |
| **Planning** | 15% of IT budget | 12-18 months | Foundation & strategy |
| **Not Started** | 8% of IT budget | Undefined | Legacy maintenance |

@notes:
- Vast majority actively engaged in transformation
- Budget allocation correlates with transformation stage
- Advanced organizations focus on innovation
- Planning stage represents growth opportunity

